        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The driver of the Kia Optima was reportedly also upset about his car, not the innocent people injured or killed. Debris from the fatal crash struck his Korean “masterpiece” and so he was upset about making an insurance claim.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
